result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleOk()"
  @cancel="handleCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="用料名称"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'name',
          {
            rules:[
              { required: true, message: '请输入用料名称' },
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.name : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="清单外"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'out_list',
          {
            rules: [
               { max:128,message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.out_list : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="合同价"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="number"
        addonAfter="万元"
        v-decorator="[
          'contract_price',
          {
            rules: [
             { required: true, message: '请输入数字' },
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.contract_price : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="变更后价"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="number"
        addonAfter="万元"
        v-decorator="[
        'change_price',
        {
          rules: [
          { required: true, message: '请输入数字' },
            { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: record ? record.change_price : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="变更前单价"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="number"
        addonAfter="元"
        v-decorator="[
        'price_before',
        {
          rules: [
            { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: record ? record.price_before : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="变更后单价"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="number"
        addonAfter="元"
        v-decorator="[
        'price_after',
        {
          rules: [
            { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: record ? record.price_after : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="变更前量"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="number"
        v-decorator="[
        'number_before',
        {
          rules: [
            { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: record ? record.number_before : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="变更后量"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="number"
        v-decorator="[
        'number_after',
        {
          rules: [
            { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: record ? record.number_after : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>

  </a-form>
</a-modal>
